high_descs: Move towards the dresser in front of the mirror then turn left and move to the corner of the room where the shopping bag is on the floor.
Pick up the tennis racket to the left of the shopping bag from the floor.
Turn around and move to the desk in the opposite corner of the room, passing by the door along the way, and then turn left and face the center of the bed.
Place the tennis racket on top of the black and white comforter in the center of the bed.
anns.task_desc: Place a tennis racket on the bed.

high_descs: Walk ahead and then turn left to the wall with the tennis racket in it.
Turn around and veer left to the side of the bed.
Place the tennis racket on the bed to the left of the pillow.
anns.task_desc: Place a tennis racket on a bed.

high_descs: Turn left, walk to the tennis bat
Grab the tennis bat from the floor
Turn around, walk to the table by the bed
Put the bat on the bed
anns.task_desc: Move the tennis bat from the floor to the bed
